      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is priced to reflect its fair condition \u2014 it's a functional, drivable car that shows noticeable signs of wear and age, both inside and out. Some cosmetic imperfections and minor mechanical attention may be expected, so it's a great fit for a handy buyer or someone who just needs reliable basic transportation without the premium price tag. What you see is what you get \u2014 honest value at an honest price!",
