    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Ready to drive home something truly special? This car is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 pristine inside and out, with every system performing flawlessly and the interior looking and smelling fresh as the day it was made. There's no wear to speak of: the paint gleams, the tech works perfectly, and the ride is as smooth and responsive as it gets. If you've been holding out for a near-perfect vehicle, your search ends here!",
