    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Practical Choice at a Fair Price! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's a reliable, functional car that gets the job done every day! You'll notice some wear on the exterior and interior that comes with a well-used vehicle, and there may be a few minor mechanical items worth addressing down the road. But the fundamentals are sound, and it drives well for everyday commuting and errands. If you're looking for honest, no-nonsense transportation without paying premium prices, this could be exactly what you need! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself. \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 buyers should understand upfront that this car has significant issues and is priced to reflect that reality. The exterior shows substantial wear including rust spots, dents, and faded paint that will require serious attention. Mechanically, the car has known problems and will likely need considerable repair work before it can be relied upon for regular use. Interior wear is heavy, with torn upholstery, damaged trim, and non-functional components. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a parts car, or willing to invest in a full restoration project. There are no hidden surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects the true state of this vehicle.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition at $32,000, and that price reflects an honest, accurate picture of what you're getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains good color and shine, though if you look closely you'll find a few minor scratches and small imperfections that come with normal use. There are no major dents or rust concerns, and the body panels are straight and solid. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional \u2014 the seats show some light wear consistent with regular use, but nothing torn or badly faded. All the main controls and features work as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs reliably and the mechanicals are in good working order \u2014 this is a car that's been used but also reasonably cared for. You can expect dependable, everyday transportation without the premium price of a mint-condition vehicle. What you see is what you get \u2014 a solid, honest used car at a fair price.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a budget-friendly, functional used car option for buyers who prioritize value over cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows visible signs of wear \u2014 multiple scratches, scuffs, and minor dents are present on various panels, and the paint has faded in certain areas. The interior is serviceable but worn, with noticeable wear on the seats, some staining on the upholstery, and general signs of heavy use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it has some age-related issues that a prospective buyer should be prepared to address \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting. All major systems are functional, but expect that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term. This is an honest, straightforward listing: the car is not in showroom shape, but it gets the job done and is priced accordingly.",
